name: SKIRT Example Styles
description:
Zand Amsterdam is a young label focusing on uniqueness and identity and bringing back colour into the world. 
Specialties are four sided wrap skirts with the following properties:
 
- A one-size-fits-most system
- A double row of snap fasteners
- Varying the upper and lower band to create various
  combinations
- Matching pouch bag for your gear

Each Skirt is unique, hand made, rich in colour, full of funky individuality and of the highest quality.
